relevant_findings.general: Alert, awake, and oriented x 3, no acute distress, calm, cooperative
relevant_findings.head_exam: Mucous membranes moist, trachea midline, extraocular movements intact
relevant_findings.chest_exam: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, normal S1/S2, no murmurs, rubs, or gallops
relevant_findings.abdominal_exam: Soft, focally tender in right lower quadrant, no guarding, no rebound, non-distended
relevant_findings.extremities_exam: Warm, well perfused, pulses palpable, no appreciable edema
